# ── Datos de backup / referencia local ───────────────────────
# JSONs pesados de Amellwind y mirror completo de 5etools (ver README)
backup-jsons/

# Mirror 5etools — solo subset para dev offline (VITE_5ETOOLS_DATA=local).
# Producción (Vercel): compendio vía GitHub; no commitear JSON extra aquí.
# races, backgrounds, feats, spells, classes, etc. → remote en prod (ver README).
public/5etools/**
!public/5etools/items.json
!public/5etools/items-base.json
!public/5etools/magicvariants.json
!public/5etools/monsterfeatures.json
!public/5etools/bestiary/
public/5etools/bestiary/**
!public/5etools/bestiary/index.json
!public/5etools/bestiary/bestiary-mm.json
!public/5etools/bestiary/legendarygroups.json
!public/5etools/bestiary/fluff-index.json
!public/5etools/bestiary/fluff-bestiary-mm.json
# Copia local opcional (gitignored): races.json, backgrounds.json, feats.json, …

